##This is a step-by-step guide on how I created my mock community

##Download FASTA files for the genomes from https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/genome/

## Use gunzip to decompress the file
$ gzip file.fna.gz

##Generate simulated dataset using ART with the specs (HiSeq 2500 (125bp, 150bp), 150 bp, paired-end, mean frag size 500, std.dev 50, #of reads 1 000 000, paired-end) 
## [options] -ss <sequencing system> -i <seq_ref_file> -l <read_length> -p <paired> -m <mean_fragment_size> -s <std_dev> -c <num_reads_per_sequences> -o <output_file_prefix> 
$ ./art_illumina -ss HS25 -i ./mock_fungal.fna -l 150 -p -m 500 -s 50 -c 1000000 -o mock_fungal_paired
